reviewText: If you are interested in postcard pictures and so cal then purchase.  There is so much more to see if this beautiful state then what was shown.  A lot of building and not enough Natural beauty.

Video was well done! I enjoyed watching this (still do). It's like a video postcard trip up and down California set to music. Sometimes, we just let the music play in the background while we are doddering around the home.

Amazing video of California . Felt like I was on a vacation in California. It was exactly like it read.. it was a video postcard. Highly recommend if you did not take enough photosof a trip to California
